name: food app mockups
description:
Food app mockups iOS UI kit consisting of 20+ pre-made but fully customizable screens. ood ordering & delivery app UI kit designed for Restaurants and food delivery shops and vendors. File includes all recent features such as Symbols or Components, Overrides, Resize Options, Text, and Layer Styles.


If you need to modify the theme you can easily change the colors and change the single elements. Only vector shapes and layer styles were used.


You can easily make this kit your own by simply modifying the text and color styles and adding your own content.


Fonts are included.
